Computational Linguistics in a Ph.D. Computer Science Program This report contains recommendations for a course curriculum on computational linguistics in  a Ph.D. computer science program.  A classification of the subject areas contained in computational linguistics  is presented, and ten courses in these areas are described.  A basic bibliography in computational linguistics  is appended. computational linguistics, mathematical linguistics, language and computer, language data processing,  computational linguistics course curriculum, computational linguistics graduate program, computational  linguistics bibliography, computer science curriculum 